Awakened Worlds: Community Edition is a volunteer-owned, non-profit Shadowrun roleplaying game. We support many types of characters, and aim to present an inclusive and welcoming environment for gamers of all types.

This being said, it should be understood that this game's rules, RP positions, and gamemaster/staff decisions are on the terms of the game's administration. We will not tolerate under any circumstances the harassment, badgering, or bullying of staff or other players out of character.

You are here on our terms.  If you disagree with our terms, disconnect now.

Welcome to Awake CE.
